  "text": "Models are evaluated using the same metrics as previous work [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . We report the test accuracy averaged over five cross validation folds [CITATION_3] for the cross-sentence n-ary relation extraction task. For the sentence-level relation extraction task, we report the micro-averaged F1 scores for the TA-CRED dataset and the macro-averaged F1 scores for the SemEval dataset [CITATION_4] .",
